description: tesapack Eco & Strong Our tesapack Eco & Strong guarantees firm, secure packaging in proven tesa quality and is at the same time an environmentally friendly alternative to conventional adhesive tapes. Ecologo certifies that this parcel tape is less harmful to the environment. Additionally, it is highly resistant to UV rays and ageing. Of course, no compromises have to be made with the reliable high adhesive strength and tear resistance of tesa. So in this case environmental friendliness and quality go hand in hand. Recommendation: for everyone who wants an environmentally friendly adhesive tape without having to give up on tape tear resistance and adhesive strength.
